<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$summer-16-26" href="/people/summer-16-26">Summer</a>，<strong title="虽然没有天生一样的，但在地球上我们是一样的。" class="zu-question-my-bio">虽然没有天生一样的，但在地球上我们是一…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="235">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-zhou-wu-di-liu-zhuang-yuan" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-zhou-wu-di-liu-zhuang-yuan" class="zg-link" title="宇宙无敌刘状元">宇宙无敌刘状元</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-yi-ming-46" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-yi-ming-46" class="zg-link" title="肖亦铭">肖亦铭</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-zhi-zhu-97" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-zhi-zhu-97" class="zg-link" title="汪致宁">汪致宁</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1470402" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix"><p>“有个女同学被人害了。班里所有人都人前人后地为她哭过，为她写过泪迹斑驳的周记。多年后恍然惊觉，那女生根本沉默寡言，没那么多友情。她死去后，就成为一块廉价而闪闪发光的肉，见者争相食之。”</p>


</div>

